    • Method Detail

      • tensor

        public abstract qlik.sse.generated.ServerSideExtension.BundledRows tensor(qlik.sse.generated.ServerSideExtension.BundledRows rows)
        Execute a tensor function. The logic that gets executed when this function is called. You must override this function in the derived class. This function is called from onNext() in the plugin.
        Parameters:
        rows - the rows that the function should execute against.
        Returns:
        an instance of BundledRows that represents the results of this execution.
